title: MisterMusic Show 347 - new indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 347 [2 hours] 192kbps MP3 -



On this week's show new music from My Sad Captains, Wire, and another new track from the latest release by ex-Supergrass singer Gaz Coombes.
Plus the 'Oldie of the Week' is a huge hit from March 1991, the highest charting single in the band's history. 
And a mix of classic hits from over 5 decades.

It's indie, alternative,and rock broadcasting globally every week-The MisterMusic Show.


The MisterMusic Show is heard weekly on RockXS internet radio.
